sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/System
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Admission Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379/TCP GCS, 8265/TCP Dashboard
    participant WorkerPod as Ray Worker Pods
    participant JobPod as Submitter Job Pod
    participant ServePod as Ray Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Redis as External Redis<br/>6379/TCP (Optional)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,WorkerPod: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate RayCluster<br/>mTLS (K8s API cert)
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: RayCluster Event

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Head Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token

        WorkerPod->>HeadPod: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP<br/>Optional Redis Password
        HeadPod->>Redis: Store GCS State<br/>Optional for FT

        Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,JobPod: Flow 2: RayJob Submission
        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>User: RayJob Created

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CRs
        K8sAPI->>Operator: RayJob Event

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create K8s Job (Submitter)<br/>ServiceAccount Token

        JobPod->>HeadPod: Submit Ray Job<br/>8265/TCP HTTP<br/>Optional Token
        JobPod->>HeadPod: Poll Job Status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
        HeadPod-->>JobPod: Job Complete
        JobPod-->>K8sAPI: Job Success
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,ServePod: Flow 3: RayService Zero-Downtime Update
        User->>K8sAPI: Update RayService CR<br/>New Version

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster v2<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Operator->>HeadPod: Deploy Serve Apps v2<br/>8265/TCP HTTP

        Operator->>ServePod: Health Check v2<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        ServePod-->>Operator: Healthy

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Service Selector<br/>Point to v2

        User->>ServePod: Inference Request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        ServePod-->>User: Response

        Operator->>K8sAPI: Delete RayCluster v1<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
        Note over HeadPod,WorkerPod: Flow 4: Autoscaling Workers
        HeadPod->>HeadPod: Monitor Resource Usage<br/>Ray Autoscaler
        HeadPod->>K8sAPI: List Worker Pods<br/>Ray SA Token
        HeadPod->>K8sAPI: Create New Worker Pods<br/>Ray SA Token

        WorkerPod->>HeadPod: Register with GCS<br/>6379/TCP
        HeadPod->>Redis: Update Worker State

        Note over HeadPod,WorkerPod: Scale Down on Idle
        HeadPod->>K8sAPI: Delete Idle Workers<br/>Ray SA Token
    end
